snippet.title: Jimmy Neutron vs. Jimmy Negatron - Full 100% Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Jimmy Neutron and his class are wandering the Retroville Museum. Suddenly, (POOF!) Jimmy finds himself in another dimension staring at HIMSELF! Kidnapped and held captive in an evil parallel dimension, Jimmy's gotta find his way back to his dimension and save the town of Retroville!

0:00:00 - Opening Cutscene
0:06:28 - Negatron Lab
0:09:10 - Ravine
0:12:41 - Wharf
0:26:21 - Underwater
0:34:12 - Negatron Lab B
0:37:57 - Museum
0:41:05 - Virtual Reality Vox
0:57:00 - Halloween
1:03:31 - Winter
1:07:07 - Independence Day
1:10:15 - Jimmy's House
1:12:19 - Pyramid
1:22:42 - Tomb A 
1:32:21 - Tomb B
1:40:45 - King Carl
1:50:04 - Flurp Factory
2:01:04 - Dinosaurs
2:05:37 - Ending

Played on a modified exe that runs the game in 1920x1080. The game's native resolution is 648x480. This walkthrough was played entirely on the HARD difficulty and shows all cinematics, uses and activates all inventions, collects all Red Neutrons (including every particle), gets the highest rank and does not take a death.

Notice that in a normal playthrough certain invention components and activators in specific levels will not spawn depending on how high your score is and what inventions you've previously unlocked. Save file manipulation and Cheat Engine were used to show where they would be in the case if the player's score is low and doesn't have the items to build a particular invention at those points.

Playlist for individual sections:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0B67TgvJMek&list=PLIQkAHrM2b8MacB9bBZu7L5LS0pOPnxDJ

Walkthrough of the demo:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1n-wyLfvXUE
